Moonsea.Geographic Features:
* [[Dragonspine Mountains]], frigid and rocky mountains that divided the region in half.
* [[Moonsea (lake)|Moonsea lake]], the vast body of water that lent its name to the surrounding lands.
* [[Twilight Marsh]], a fog-covered swamp{{Cite adventurers league/Drums in the Marsh|14}} that was home to [[lizardfolk]] and the terrible [[black dragon]] [[Throstulgrael]].{{Cite adventurers league/Drums in the Marsh|5}}
